INSERT INTO `hesk_tickets` VALUES (181, '8JUT688UZJ', 'Silke Schnell', 's.schnell@seel-ilsfeld.de', 2, '1', 'Brochure Request/Visitor Centre', 'Your website may be helpful for research online, but it is impossible to find information about Tourist Centres and also impossible to order a brochure. The mechanism may work but the information must be lost somewhere in cyberspace because after ordering a brochure twice I still have not received one yet and I have also failed to find a contact e-mail address and/or telephone number for direct enquiries. What a shame!!!', '2010-11-02 13:09:37', '2010-11-02 14:03:06', '91.49.140.158', '3', '1', '0', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '');
